<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Version-Conflict on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/version-conflict/</link><description>Recent content in Version-Conflict on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/version-conflict/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Dependency resolution failed</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/flutter/flutter-dependency-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/flutter/flutter-dependency-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when the Dart package resolver cannot find a set of compatible package versions that satisfy all version constraints in &lt;code&gt;pubspec.yaml&lt;/code&gt; and their transitive dependencies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Two packages require conflicting versions of the same transitive dependency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A package was discontinued or removed from pub.dev&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Circular dependency between packages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lower bound of a dependency exceeds the version available&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pre-release versions conflicting with stable constraints&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run &lt;code&gt;dart pub deps&lt;/code&gt; to inspect the dependency tree:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;dart pub deps
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;dart pub upgrade&lt;/code&gt; to find the latest compatible versions:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;dart pub upgrade --major-versions
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pin specific versions or use &lt;code&gt;dependency_overrides&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;dependency_overrides&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Temporary override while waiting for upstream fix&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;transitive_package&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2.1.0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remove or replace incompatible packages:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Before — conflict&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;dependencies&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;package_a&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;^1.0.0 &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# requires http ^0.12.0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;package_b&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;^3.0.0 &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# requires http ^1.0.0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# After — find alternatives&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;dependencies&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;package_a&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;^2.0.0 &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# updated — now compatible&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;package_b&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;^3.0.0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Because every version of package_a depends on http ^0.13.0 and package_b &amp;gt;=3.0.0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;depends on http ^1.0.0, package_a is incompatible with package_b.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=""&gt;Pub error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flutter/build-error6/"&gt;Build error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>